    "description": "Button trigger that opens an ActionMenu overlay for presenting a list of selectable actions or options. Composes an ArvoButton trigger with an ArvoActionMenu panel. Supports action mode (fire-and-forget item activation) and selection mode (selected item updates the button label and marks the item active).",
